I would like to say that HL2:Ep1 is such extraordinary as his precursor: i can't. Don't get me wrong, this is an amazing game by all means, but it lacks in innovation. It feels like only more HL2 (what is not bad) and i was expecting something fresh.
Despite this, HL2:Ep1 is a great game and has so much quality as HL2. It is more story driven and does a really good job in this field.
Positives:

+ More history development;
+ The characters are well developed.
+ Pretty much so awesome as HL2.

Negatives:

- It's a little too short;
- Lacks in innovation;

9.5/10 - It's great and a deserved sequel!
